About the Author

Michael Doyle, MCTS, MCSD, MCSE, is a senior architect at a major company who has been working with SharePoint for more than a decade. Michael is the author of Microsoft SharePoint 2010: Customizing My Site and a coauthor of Microsoft SharePoint Foundation 2010 Inside Out.
